data.description: This well maintained home is an absolute must see! The home features 3 large bedrooms and 2 full baths. The isolated master bedroom has vaulted ceilings, with new countertops and a tiled tub/shower combo. On the other side of the home you have 2 large bedrooms and a recently updated bathroom. All upgrades in the home include, fresh paint throughout, new vanities in both bathrooms, walk in shower in guest bathroom, new carpet in all bedrooms, new light fixtures in master bedroom and first guest bedroom. New light fixtures and backsplash in kitchen as well as a new dishwasher and stove, fireplace freshly painted with new mantle, fascia and soffit in the back of the house was replaced. The home is located within the city of Hewitt so this home makes for the perfect investment property for your portfolio as it can be used as an air bnb or long term rental. Call today to see this lovely home in person
